<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUS, THE VERY THOUGHT OF THEE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu Na thu ka ngaihtuoh in,
 Ka kipahna alien;
 Na mel tak chu ka hun muh tieng,
 Ka lawpna sang in a

[V2]
 2. Khawvel aw hawih chengcheng ahin,
 Gihawih tincheng lak ah;
 Mihing Hukdampa Na min hi,
 Ngaihnawp ka sapen hi.

[V3]
 3. Kisikte lungmuonna Na hi,
 Liengvaite lawpna tawh;
 Kipukte chung ale Na pha'i,
 Nang hun hawlte chung ah.

[V4]
 4. Nang hun mu ta'n a lawpzie chu,
 Thu'n a hun gen theipuou;
 Isu, Na hehpihna lien hi,
 Nang hun gingte'n a muu.

[V5]
 5. Isu ka kipahna pen hi'n,
 Ka kipahman u hi'n;
 Isu ka suonpen uh hi'n tu'n,
 Kumsawt mun chan inle.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>37</hymn_number>
</song>